                            <comment id="14638644" author="tmgstev" created="Thu, 23 Jul 2015 11:11:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is not just external tables - any tables where users are directly modifying the underlying data can be impacted by this.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
